{"tid":2225752,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"從文明中心到全球最大死城，認識阿塞拜疆與亞美尼亞戰爭","createTime":"2020-10-01T14:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T12:43:31.000Z","uid":51620,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9db74f05067529b1259086ea2aa0c80bb92f86","tid":2225752,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:13:45.000Z","msg":"最近多處地緣政局劍拔弩張，南高加索也再起戰幔，阿塞拜疆與亞美尼亞日前就主權爭議開戰。這兩個前蘇聯國家的領土一直「你中有我、我中有你」，30 多年前已經爆發戰爭，上演多場令人髮指的殺戮，遺下一座全球最大死城、一道可見的戰爭疤痕，並為今日戰事留下伏筆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/shutterstock_1025476606-scaled-e1601301615252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fshutterstock_1025476606-scaled-e1601301615252.jpg&h=a38170d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人口曾經達 5 萬的阿塞拜疆地方首府阿格達姆，如今已淪為全球最大死城。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/09/29/azerbaijan-and-armenia-clash/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2020%2F09%2F29%2Fazerbaijan-and-armenia-clash%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2FMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=a0934533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/09/29/azerbaijan-and-armenia-clash/</a>"},{"pid":"e7d95a1c4e5a76e7fa213e6af73ed6a95bc73cdc","tid":2225752,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:32:06.000Z","msg":"明日香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771d9b42a8258c33613de72de94b1f038601013a","tid":2225752,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0dda94a2a7ee9d93fb9047de92d188b38db221","tid":2225752,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"呢個位算唔算係小歷細亞一部分?"},{"pid":"018e09455718574b92fe37056c27f126